OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing during the evening, then
OL,7,Fclouding over from the west with rain
OL,8,Farriving during the early hours and
OL,9,Flasting the rest of the night. Feeling
OL,10,Fcold in the strengthening
OL,11,Fsoutheasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with early
OL,14,Frain slowly clearing to the east
OL,15,Ffollowed by frequent heavy showers in
OL,16,Fthe afternoon and well into the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
